
README


0. files

 rulebook_chap4parsed.txt: Chapter 4(stage I tests) text parsed by Brill POS tagger
 all_verbs_in_chap4.txt: all possible verbs extracted from Chapter 4
 robot_related_verbs_in_chap4.txt: robot-related-verbs extracted from all_verbs_in_chap4.txt

 cat1Sentences.txt: generated sentences by make_sentence.pl 
 make_sentences.pl: sentence generator for category I sentences
 GPSR1.gram : defines sentence templates 

1. how to generate category I sentences
$ ./make_sentences.pl

